channel.title: Leaving
channel.description:
Leaving threads,
Stop them, we honestly don't care if they are not against the rules.
You will eventually come back. [b][i]If[/i][/b] you think you can actually leave, put it in your signature. They aren't against the rules, but think. If you are going to come back anyway, why do you need the attention of a thread.
[b][i]You can't leave moparscape. We own your soul.[/i][/b]
discuss.
